  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combine The Five Elements</h2>In the game you play as a <strong>fish wizard</strong> that has the ability to combine elements into different spells:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1637140/extras/ae113251081df3f6ab2f0c30fa2d1bd1.avif?t=1673028336\" width=415 height=119 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intense, Wacky, Skill-shot PVP!</h2>Learn which elements combine into what spell, how to switch between spells quickly and become a <strong>dominating force!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1637140/extras/5f10a086348fe047a765edc1dd11dd61.poster.avif?t=1673028336\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1637140/extras/5f10a086348fe047a765edc1dd11dd61.webm?t=1673028336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1637140/extras/5f10a086348fe047a765edc1dd11dd61.mp4?t=1673028336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gorgeous Graphics</h2>Fishards looks like a 2D game, however, it’s really just 3D models rendered in low resolution and scaled up!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1637140/extras/fec420060faabe3c9abf9a08e25fc598.poster.avif?t=1673028336\" width=770 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1637140/extras/fec420060faabe3c9abf9a08e25fc598.webm?t=1673028336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1637140/extras/fec420060faabe3c9abf9a08e25fc598.mp4?t=1673028336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
